Class SpaceShip

  • java.lang.Object
    • SpaceShip
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Aggressive, Basher, Drunkard, Human, Runner, Special
    public abstract class SpaceShip
extends java.lang.Object
    The API spaceships need to implement for the SpaceWars game. It is your decision whether SpaceShip.java will be an interface, an abstract class, a base class for the other spaceships or any other option you will choose.
